6:
Ahaha... AHAHAHA! You guys ain't too 
bad, for a bunch of lizards!
11:
See, I don't got time to play with you 
small fries anymore... I've got buds are 
waitin' for me now!
16:
Ahaha! If you're even THINKIN' about 
gettin' past me, you'll have to answer 
to this blade first!
18:
Get ready to meet your maker, 
and tell 'em who sent ya!
32:
Sup, Stella. Sorry about the face...
It took a few licks too many out there.
43: Haha! Way to go with the flow, girl!
47:
Phew, I didn't think you'd go to an 
entirely different world. Just how good 
are these herbs?
55: A scavenger hunt? Count me in!
60:
I now understand why cats are afraid 
of heights.
64:
Ahaha! You know what they say about 
curiosity... But don't worry! I'll catch ya!
71:
No worries. I guess you're the type to 
act first and think later, huh?
75:
By the way, what are these herbs even 
supposed to look like? I don't even 
know what I'm supposed to be lookin' 
for.
82:
Ahahaha! That's okay, too. Lead the 
way!
87:
Fun factsitting with your back to 
a fire will actually keep you warm 
longer.
90: Fascinating. Where did you learn that?
93:
Back in the day before the church 
started helping us out, I had to look 
after my li'l bro at the orphanage. 
You pick up a thing or two.
96:
And I've gotta hand it to you, Stella. 
I thought I was reckless, but it looks like 
I've got competition.
99:
...I just follow what my heart tells me to 
do.
103:
Hah! I like that. Not a lot of people 
have the nerve to do that, ya know?
106:
Take me, for example. Some people 
might think I'm just a loose cannon, 
but even I have my own rules.
109:
Rule one! I NEVER involve any innocent 
bystanders. Rule two! I ALWAYS 
apologize for any mess that I make.
111:
These rules have served me well 
throughout the years. I bet you'd do 
well to remember 'em.
114:
Is that why you're always so patient 
with me?
119:
Nothing like the thrill of survival to 
make you appreciate your next meal. 
But if someone were to bite the dust 
on my watch? Not so much.
121:
So when it comes to the risky stuff, 
just leave it to me. Got it?
129:
Aha! That's the herb we've been 
looking for!
134: Indeed. Please use them on your face.
138:
Wait... These were for me?
Aw, Stella, you shouldn't have! This 
wound right here ain't nothin' a little 
spit can't handle!
145:
Not one for a lot of words, are ya?
But if you insist, I'll save 'em for next 
time.
148:
They'll be perfect for when I find the 
ultimate foe in a REAL deathmatch for 
the ages!
Uh... Ahem. I mean, are we done here?
